query:
SELECT
                    COALESCE(packets_received, 0) as packets_received,
                    COALESCE(packets_sent, 0) as packets_sent,
                    COALESCE(packets_dropped, 0) as packets_dropped
                FROM nym_nodes_packet_stats_raw
                WHERE node_id = ?
                ORDER BY timestamp_utc DESC
                LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1
